In the MATTER OF the Suspension or Revocation of the License of: Steven C. BRIGHAM, M.D. License No. MA05106800 To Practice Medicine and Surgery in the State of New Jersey. (Steven C. Brigham, M.D. - Petitioner) C-640 September Term 2018
081912 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 8, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001944-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
